Text: LSU Game watchWatch the Tigers Wreck the Rebels LSU vs Ole Miss October pm Come watch at Woodrows under the big tent Note that parking will be available in the office building next door as well as the normal areas coming from Richmond go past the office building next to Woodrows and take a right to get to the parking garage Parking is available for cars and small SUVs due to clearance restrictions large vehicles are not allowed to park in the garage For those unable to make it to Woodrows Nicks Place will be showing the game as well Also for our travelling Tigers note the following construction update from La DOTD DOTD is doing roadwork on I around the Hwy area in Jeff Davis Parish Houstonarea Tiger fans should be advised to take evasive manueversie exit Iowa and head south to Hwy go east on to Welsh and then back to I See the link construcmapaspprojectjeffdav This message contains information that may be privileged or confidential and is the property of the Cap Gemini Ernst Young Group It is intended only for the person to whom it is addressed If you are not the intended recipient you are not authorized to read print retain copy disseminate distribute or use this message or any part thereof If you receive this message in error please notify the sender immediately and delete all copies of this message
